    tf.keras.layers.Dense(300, activation="relu", name="hiddenLayer01"), # 300

    tf.keras.layers.Dense(CLASSES, activation="softmax", name="outputLayer"), # 10

        labels[idx] = np.where(label%2 == 0, 1, 0) # 1 -> even, 0 -> odd
    return labels
